SUBSTANCE PAPER
*DESCRIPTION_START READ ITEM -1
The Prophecy of the Wolf
       Recorded by
    Samardaz Wereslayer
	Farnum 715


Be wary for in the time of the rat
it is ordained that the man who is
a wolf shall meet the wolf that is
not a wolf.

Five there are that must accompany
the chosen one. The companions are
to be chosen carfully for only the
true six may defeat the terror that
shall rise.

The scaly one who shall give its
life willingly. He alone can be the
sacrifice no other may serve.

The one with no flesh for only one
of that race may survive the ordeal.
No harm shall befall this one in its
task.

The short one who will stop the magic
that opposes the companions. Only one
of this race has a hope of completing
this task.

The one who walks in darkness for only
such a one can pass the gate so the rest
may follow. The actions of this one will
surprise all.

The normal one whose roll must not and
can not be revealed. To do so would be
to thwart all hope of success.

The man that is a wolf will use that
which has not been used since the time
of the last ending. The wolf who is not
a wolf shall use only what it has.

The struggle rests upon these and others
with smaller yet no less important roles
to play. The outcome undecided until all
tasks are accomplished.
*DESCRIPTION_END
