IFPREVERB exa -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER This compact crossbow has two bow-strings and two slots for crossbow bolts side by side. Although it is small and compact, the crossbow itself is made out of a strange metal with metalic looking strings. This is most certainly no ordinary crossbow.
	IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 0
		ECHO PLAYER The crossbow is currently unloaded.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 1
		ECHO PLAYER The double crossbow currently has one bolt loaded into it.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR ITEMVAL3 = 2
		ECHO PLAYER The double crossbow is fully loaded.
	ENDIF
